# Nyora Desktop — Supabase + Google sync configuration.
#
# Read at startup by the shared engine's SupabaseConfig.load() from the working
# directory, overriding the baked defaults. Precedence: env var > .env.sync >
# supabase.properties (data dir) > baked. Active profile = production. To use a
# local Supabase, comment the production block and uncomment the development
# block, then relaunch.

# --- Production (active) ---
